config MT7927
	tristate "MediaTek MT7927 (Filogic 380) Wi-Fi 7 PCIe support"
	depends on PCI && MAC80211
	help
	  This is an experimental, reverse-engineered driver for the
	  MediaTek MT7927 (Filogic 380) Wi-Fi 7 PCIe chipset.
	  
	  PCI ID: 14C3:7927
	  
	  This driver is NOT official and is based on reverse engineering
	  efforts. Use at your own risk. It may not work correctly and
	  could potentially damage hardware.
	  
	  The driver is modeled after the mt76 driver family but is
	  independent and experimental.
	  
	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here. The module
	  will be called mt7927.
	  
	  If unsure, say N.
